			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong><a href="http://www.simner.com/">By Janni Lee Simner.</a></strong><br />
Read by: <a href="http://murverse.com/">Mur Lafferty</a><br />
First appeared in the anthology <em>Not Of Woman Born</em><br />
<a href="http://forum.escapeartists.net/index.php?board=1.0">Discuss on our forums.</a><br />
